<div style="width: 103px; height: 165px; background-color: white; float: left;"><img alt="BYU-Idaho Student" height="165" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Participate_Activities/girl_purple_shirt_sm.jpg" width="103" /></div>
<div style="position: relative; width: 548px; height: 165px; background-color: white; float: left;">
<div style="width: 548px; height: auto; background-color: white; padding: 23px 0px 5px 5px;"><img alt="Discover Activities Header Text" height="75" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Participate_Activities/participate_activities_header_text.png" width="546" /></div>
<div style="width: 548px; height: 1px; background-color: #858585;"></div>
<div style="width: 548px; height: auto; background-color: white; padding: 5px 0px 5px 2px;"><span style="font-family: georgia; font-size: 20px; line-height: 29px; font-style: italic; color: #969696;">The Activities Program is led entirely by students like you! There are thousands of opportunities to get involved as a leader, volunteer or participant. Every BYU-Idaho student is invited to apply in any area they are interested in. </span></div>
<div style="width: 548px; height: 1px; background-color: #858585;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="position: relative; width: 651px; height: 100%; background-color: white; clear: both; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 35px; margin-left: 107px;">
<div style="width: 450px; height: 100%; background-color: white; float: left; padding-right: 20px;"><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino; font-size: medium;">There are seven different areas of the Activities Program with five levels of leadership structure divided into each. Click the image to the right for an interactive look at the student leadership and volunteer structure.</span></div>
<div style="width: 140px; height: 100%; background-color: white; float: left;"><a href="x34041.xml" title="Student Leadership &amp; Volunteer Structure"><img alt="Student Leadership Structure" height="100" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Participate_Activities/student_leadership_flash_link.gif" width="100" /></a></div>
</div>
<div style="position: relative; width: 651px; height: 100%; background-color: white; clear: both; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 60px; margin-left: 107px;">
<div style="width: 550px; height: 100%; background-color: white; float: left;">
<p style="font-family: georgia, palatino; font-size: medium;">To apply for a manager, coordinator or director position in the Activities Program, or if you'd prefer to volunteer at an event, please contact the Activities Department for further information or see our "Activities Get Involved" page in the left navigation for application links.</p>
<p style="font-family: georgia, palatino; font-size: medium;">Information on how to be a participant in an event can be found in the Student Activities menu on the left by clicking on the respective area of Activities.</p>
